Finally, the year ended with a ray of home that the world is on the cusp of containing the Covid-19 pandemic following the discovery of vaccines. But the big question is whether developing countries will have equitable access to the vaccines. Court says NCBA bank is entitled to exercise its power of sale to recover the money. Cars registered in 2013 arriving after December 31 will not be rejected at importer’s cost. Our source says security officials had been briefed the DP was coming.